				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">IM &amp; SM Questions<a name="27882"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Mar 15 04 4:31 PM</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>Hey guys,
<br />

<br />
Im curious about some stuff concerning these AA's
<br />

<br />
First off Does IM Still Effect Songs that specify an instrument but you dont have that instrument equiped.  Ex. If your Singing Selo's without a drum, would IM still give you a boost?
<br />

<br />
And if It doesn't give a boost then does Singing Mastery Effect all songs that you sing without an instrument or just the ones that are specified as Singing.  Ex. If your Singing Selos without a Drum would SM gives you the Boost?
<br />

<br />
And if there is anything else you can add to help clarify this for me please do = )
<br />

<br />
Thanks Guys
<br />

<br />
Mastton</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
